                <li>Toronto property tax lien</li>
                <li>Snowbirds vacant home tax</li>
                <li>Change of ownership VHT</li>
                <li>Vacant home tax fine $10,000</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection
      title="Buying or selling a Toronto property?"
      body="I check Vacant Home Tax declaration status on every Toronto listing I represent — as a seller, as a buyer, and everything in between. If closing is coming up and the VHT paperwork is unclear, that's exactly the kind of question worth catching before signing."
      ctaPrimary={{ href: '/contact', label: 'Talk to Peter' }}
      ctaSecondary={{ href: '/blog', label: 'More Toronto guides' }}
    />
  </article>

